      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. can u get a bit more specific about hair and makeup though? like, what kind of hair styles or grooming habits are considered the most \"standard\" or safe for an executive level to ensure they aren't seen as too casual or distracting? i want to make sure they stick to the professional norm.",
